      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِذَا دَفَنْتَ فِي اَلْأَرْضِ شَيْئاً فَأَشْهِدْ عَلَيْهَا فَإِنَّهَا لاَ تُؤَدِّي إِلَيْكَ شَيْئاً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3364 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"If you bury something in the ground, have witnesses for it, for the earth will not return anything to you.\""
        ]
      }
